ue\">&gt;</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color:Blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">WPFToolkit</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">DataGridComboBoxColumn</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color:Blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">WPFToolkit</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">DataGrid.Columns</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span><br><span style=\"color:Blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">WPFToolkit</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#A31515\">DataGrid</span><span style=\"color:Blue\">&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Any suggestions?</span></p>",
